  <brief_title>European Organisation of Research and Treatment (EORTC) Quality of Life Questionnaire (QLQ) Breast Cancer Module Update</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Update of the EORTC Quality of Life Questionnaire Breast Cancer Module (EORTC QLQ-Breast 23) Phase 1-3</official_title>
  <sponsors>
